[I] Cloud instance initialization

[T] Cloud-init is the industry standard multi-distribution method for
[T] cross-platform cloud instance initialization. It is supported across all
[T] major public cloud providers, provisioning systems for private cloud
[T] infrastructure, and bare-metal installations.

[U] https://github.com/canonical/cloud-init

